Description: Implements S-type ridge regression, a robust and multicollinearity-aware linear regression estimator that combines S-type robust weighting (via the Stype.est package) with ridge penalization; automatically selects the ridge parameter using the ridgregextra approach targeting near-1 VIF, and returns comprehensive outputs (coefficients, fitted values, residuals, MSE etc.) with an easy x/y interface and optional user-supplied weights.
